Padding

INSTRUCTIONS: Style the #box div to have padding of 15px on the top, right, bottom and left sides with as few commands as you can.

<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Padding</title>
        <style type="text/css">   
			#box {
            }
        </style>
        </head>
    <body>
		<div id="box">Box</div>
    </body>
</html>


Answer:
<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Padding</title>
        <style type="text/css">   
			#box {
			    padding: 15px;
            }
        </style>
        </head>
    <body>
		<div id="box">Box</div>
    </body>
</html>